name: Princess Zelda | The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom
description:
Princess Zelda from Tears of the Kingdom. Trained at 768x768 using in-game cutscenes.

KEEP THE WEIGHT AROUND 0.75.

I just beat the game and HAD to make my own LoRA, I don't mind if there already are others. I just love the game so much! The ending was incredible and I hope you enjoy the game as well.

Anyways, this LoRA turned out BEAUTIFUL. I used a lot of images with GREAT lighting so that Princess Zelda SHINES beautifully.

I ONLY used images where she is wearing that new Zonai dress we see her wearing since the beginning of the game.

Made using Derrian's Easy Training Scripts

Here's a list of words you can add to your prompt straight from the training dataset:

  • jewelry

  • earrings

  • pointy ears

  • bare shoulders

  • necklace

  • braid

  • strapless

  • crown braid

  • triforce

  • strapless dress

  • collarbone

  • hair ornament

  • outdoors

  • bracelet

  • alternate costume

  • alternate hairstyle

  • thick eyebrows
